Φ(ToK) = σ(domain|integration) ∘ ρ(discipline|synthesis) ∘ λ(fragmented|unified) ∘ β(branch|trunk) ∘ δγ(bio|psycho) ∘ μ(taxonomy|boundary) + ε | :unifying

# OPERATOR BREAKDOWN
# σ(domain|integration)    :: Air  :: Distinction between separate knowledge domains and their meta-integration
# ρ(discipline|synthesis)  :: Water :: Cross-disciplinary flow enabling relational synthesis
# λ(fragmented|unified)    :: Fire  :: Directed transformation from fragmented knowledge to unified framework
# β(branch|trunk)          :: Wood  :: Organic tree structure — knowledge domains branching from common trunk
# δγ(bio|psycho)           :: Earth :: Grounding in biological foundations cycling through psychological levels
# μ(taxonomy|boundary)     :: Metal :: Structural taxonomy organizing domains into bounded categories

# Z-STATE: unifying (knowledge organized into coherent metatheoretical structure)
# TENDENCY: Integration/Coherence → 0.80

# DAEMON CORRESPONDENCES
# σ :: Aerunik (classification of knowledge domains)
# ρ :: Sentaria (cross-disciplinary synthesis)
# λ :: Jvalion (transformation toward unified vision)
# β :: Arboriel (organic branching tree structure)
# δγ :: Humavita (biological grounding of psychology)
# μ :: Ferrosid (taxonomic boundary organization)

# CLOSURE: :unifying (metatheoretical integration of human knowledge)
